  "title": "Packer (Laundry) #76202",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Laundry</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Packer (Laundry)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Pioneer</li><li>Working Hours: 6 days (Mon – Sat : 9am – 6pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Transport Allowance + OT Pay</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Steam, iron, and blow garments.</li><li>Use steam presses to shape garments and remove or add creases.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness of the work area and equipment.</li><li>Perform quality checks on garments before packaging and delivery.</li><li>Pay close attention to details and garment quality.</li><li>Work efficiently, manage time well, and support team members.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Candidates with experience in pressing or ironing are encouraged to apply.</li><li>Training will be provided.</li><li>Able to start work at short notice is an advantage.</li><li>Open to working overtime if required (overtime pay is provided).</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#76202 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
